Node.Description: Go to Sales and marketing > Periodic tasks > Automated order completion.
Expand the Records to include section.
In the list, mark the selected row.
In the Field field, enter or select a value.
In the list, click the link in the selected row.
In the Criteria field, enter or select a value.
In the Criteria field, type a value.
In the PatternUnit field, select an option.
In the Count field, enter a number.
Select the No end date option.
In the Start date field, enter a date.
In the Start time field, enter a time.
